    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The primary standard for time used by most of the world to regulates clocks and time. It is within about 1 second of mean solar time at 0 degree longitude; it is not adjusted for daylight saving time.</Note_Text>
